    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对乌克兰保持压力，因为普京对停火开放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-keeps-pressure-on-ukraine-as-putin-seen-open-to-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对乌克兰（Ukraine）的压力保持了一项和平协议的压力，因为信号表明克里姆林宫愿意在某些条件下接受临时休战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-keeps-pressure-on-ukraine-as-putin-seen-open-to-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 22:09:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法院顾问说，亚当斯案件应永久抛弃。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/adams-case-should-be-permanently-dismissed-court-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名律师说，对纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）的刑事指控应被驳回，而无需将其提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/adams-case-should-be-permanently-dismissed-court-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 22:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊总理三菱在议会中幸存下来的谴责动议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/greek-pm-mitsotakis-survives-censure-motion-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理吉里亚科斯·西塔基斯（Kyriakos Mitsotakis）周五晚些时候在议会中赢得了一项谴责动议，在批评两年前对希腊最致命的火车撞车事故的批评之后，赢得了对政府的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/greek-pm-mitsotakis-survives-censure-motion-in-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 21:38:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱迪生首席执行官说，关税风险提高电费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/california-utility-ceo-says-tariffs-risk-raising-electric-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱迪生国际（Edison International）的高管表示，特朗普政府在洛杉矶地区野火之后重建了该系统的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/california-utility-ceo-says-tariffs-risk-raising-electric-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 21:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普以4亿美元的联邦赠款削减了反犹太主义的奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-hits-columbia-with-400-million-in-cuts-over-antisemitism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府将取消4亿美元的联邦赠款和哥伦比亚大学的合同，理由是自10月7日哈马斯对以色列的袭击以来，犹太学生的反犹太主义投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-hits-columbia-with-400-million-in-cuts-over-antisemitism</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:50:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在创建美国比特币储备后认可稳定币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/us-to-start-audit-of-current-crypto-holdings-white-house-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）承诺在下令创建美国战略比特币储备金和单独的其他数字资产的库存之后，在周五为立法努力构成Stablecoins的立法努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/us-to-start-audit-of-current-crypto-holdings-white-house-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 16:03:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
